an></p></td></tr><tr class="c19"><td class="c17" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c1 c4"><span class="c3">Analytics cookies</span></p></td><td class="c16" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c1 c4"><span class="c3">We do this so that we can constantly improve the user experience and fix any problems there might be on the website or Mobile Applications</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p class="c1 c14"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c1 c14"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c1 c14"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3">Functionality</span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3">We use the following functionality cookies:</span></p><a id="t.33234c43f5bf8819f576b5a5b5e2ad7021cbdadd"></a><a id="t.4"></a><table class="c20"><tbody><tr class="c25"><td class="c26" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c1 c4"><span class="c2">Description of Cookie</span></p></td><td class="c21" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c1 c4"><span class="c2">Purpose</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c19"><td class="c26" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c1 c4"><span class="c3">functional cookies</span></p></td><td class="c21" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c1 c4"><span class="c3">to remember choices you made or information you provided, such as your username, language, or the region you are in.</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p class="c1 c14"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c1 c14"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c1 c14"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3">Targeting</span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3">We use the following targeting cookies:</span></p><a id="t.822fd063dc0f82eaf82181e35ab2cd245d238d1e"></a><a id="t.5"></a><table class="c20"><tbody><tr class="c25"><td class="c26" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c1 c4"><span class="c2">Description of Cookie</span></p></td><td class="c21" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c1 c4"><span class="c2">Purpose</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c23"><td class="c26" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p c